The Tutorial TA duties will consist of:
- Delivering 4 hours of problem-solving tutorials each week;
- Grading a midterm test and two quizzes for a class of approximately 80 students;
- Invigilating quizzes and midterm;
- Holding weekly office hours for students;
- Answering student emails and meeting with the course instructor.

qualifications_minimum:
The candidate must preferably have: 
- Taken this or a similar course in the past;
- Acquired experience teaching and/or tutoring students;
- Shown excellence in teaching/public speaking.

